milestones.description: Benjamin and Carl Hooper's 65-run partnership is WI's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 59 between Viv Richards and Baptiste
Kapil Dev and Ravi Shastri's 113-run partnership is IND's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 104 between Kapil Dev and Ravi Shastri
Maninder Singh and Kiran More's 38-run partnership is IND's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 27 between Srinivas Venkataraghavan and Bishan Bedi
